---
layout: base.njk
title: "Home"
description: "A technical blog about software development, authentication, and technology insights."
---

<div class="hero">
    <h1>Welcome to formyfelleows</h1>
    <p>Just write - A technical blog exploring software development, authentication protocols, and technology insights.</p>
</div>

<section class="recent-posts">
    <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
    
    {% if collections.posts.length > 0 %}
        <div class="posts-grid">
            {% for post in collections.posts.slice(0, 6) %}
                <article class="post-card">
                    <header class="post-card-header">
                        <h3 class="post-card-title">
                            <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                        </h3>
                        <div class="post-card-meta">
                            <time datetime="{{ post.date | date('Y-m-d') }}">
                                {{ post.date | dateFilter }}
                            </time>
                            <span class="reading-time">{{ post.templateContent | readingTime }}</span>
                        </div>
                    </header>
                    
                    {% if post.data.description %}
                    <p class="post-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                    
                    {% if post.data.tags %}
                    <div class="post-card-tags">
                        {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                            {% if tag != "post" %}
                            <span class="tag">#{{ tag }}</span>
                            {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                    
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card-link">Read more â†’</a>
                </article>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        
        {% if collections.posts.length > 6 %}
        <div class="view-all">
            <a href="/posts/" class="btn">View All Posts</a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
    {% else %}
        <p>No posts yet. Check back soon!</p>
    {% endif %}
</section>

<section class="about-preview">
    <h2>About This Blog</h2>
    <p>This blog focuses on technical topics in software development, with a particular interest in authentication protocols like OAuth 2.0, Keycloak, and modern web technologies. Each post aims to break down complex concepts into understandable explanations.</p>
    <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
</section>